word_mean_info__list.difference: 指在需要时可以动用的财产，包括国家土地、矿藏、水力等自然资源或个人的存款及其他财产。
法律和商业用词，指包括全部动产和不动产的资产。
含义较窄，主要指个人动产。
普通用词，含义广。既可指大笔的钱财或物质财富，也可指抽象的精神财富。
含义较estate宽，指个人或团体合法拥有的财产，包括动产与不动产，或临时的财产。
多指地产或建在地面上的房产。

bilingual.source: She invested her beni in real estate.
bilingual.target: 她将她的财产投资于房地产。

bilingual.source: He is profiting by investing in real estate.
bilingual.target: 他通过投资房地产获利。

bilingual.source: Their asset mainly comes from real estate.
bilingual.target: 他们的身家主要来自房地产。

bilingual.source: He dreams of becoming a real estate tycoon.
bilingual.target: 他梦想成为一名房地产财阀。

bilingual.source: He counseled his friend to invest in real estate.
bilingual.target: 他建议朋友投资房地产。

bilingual.source: Many people invest in the real estate market.
bilingual.target: 许多人在房地产市场中投资。

bilingual.source: Real estate does not usually depreciate quickly.
bilingual.target: 房地产通常不会迅速折旧。

bilingual.source: They reinvested the capital into real estate.
bilingual.target: 他们将资本再投资到房地产中。

bilingual.source: John invests in real estate to build his wealth.
bilingual.target: 约翰投资房地产来积累财富。

yingyinNormal.en: Real estate? Oh. And you know who's selling a great apartment? Richard!
yingyinNormal.zh: 房地产，是吗？你知道谁要卖一间很棒的公寓吗？理查！

yingyinNormal.en: Power is a lot like real estate. Remember? So help me God. So help me God.
yingyinNormal.zh: 权力和房地产很像。还记得吗？愿上帝助我。愿上帝助我。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, it's great being a real estate agent, my face is on billboards and pens.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当一名房地产中介挺好的，我的脸被印在广告牌和笔上。

yingyinNormal.en: That's totally understandable. In bladder voiding, as in real estate, it's location, location, location.
yingyinNormal.zh: 非常能理解，排空膀胱，就好像搞房地产，地点最重要。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. There he is. Hey. You. How long's it been, Mr. Real estate? Well, you tell me, Mr. You.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是你啊。你好啊。有多久没见了，房地产先生？你说呢，这位先生。

yingyinNormal.en: During the real estate boom, markets were going up and up and people thought they would never go down.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在房地产繁荣时期，市场持续火热，人们就认为房价再也不会下跌。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. What? Do you have to be a Century 21 real-estate agent to get to wear those really cool jackets?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，干嘛？一定要当21世纪的房地产经纪人才能穿着那么酷的外套吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Joey, I think you should consider something a little less risky. I mean, I think in this market, real estate is your best investment.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你应该考虑比较低风险性的投资，我认为房地产会是最好的投资。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm very pleased the estate can afford such a living.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很高兴你们能过好日子。

yingyinNormal.en: So, the bequest stands? Yes. Mary owns half the estate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，他的意愿有效？是的，玛丽拥有一半的庄园财产。

yingyinNormal.en: As for managing the estate, I wouldn't know where to start.
yingyinNormal.zh: 至于管理庄园，我不知从何下手。

yingyinNormal.en: My father managed his estate. We grew up together, Darcy and I.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我父亲是他家的账房先生。我们从小一起长大，达西和我。

yingyinNormal.en: Real estate must be pretty cheap around here. Wow, this is incredible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里的房价一定非常低吧！哇哦，真是不可思议。

yingyinNormal.en: My father and I co-own the estate. But I really function as the agent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我和父亲共同拥有庄园，但我其实是作为代理人。

yingyinNormal.en: What? It's prime real estate. Everything else in Williamsburg is taken.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了，这可是风水宝地啊，星巴克在Williamsburg已经无孔不入了。

yingyinNormal.en: And I had to drop off some papers for Shelly to sign for my dad's estate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还过来让谢利在父亲的地产文书上签个字。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, if George is owner of half the estate now, shouldn't you represent him?
yingyinNormal.zh: 既然乔治现在拥有一半庄园，难道你不该代表他吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Of course she is, but when it comes to decisions about the estate, shouldn't it be me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然了，但是涉及到关于庄园的决定，我来不是更妥当吗？

yingyinNormal.en: There's no way the real estate agent could've seen me moving any product on February 25.
yingyinNormal.zh: 房产中介不可能看到我在25号搬运任何东西。

yingyinNormal.en: Explain the crops and the livestock. You know, let her see the problems facing the estate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 教她认庄稼还有牲口，让她明白庄园现在的问题所在。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: HGTV has seriously changed how people view real <highlight>estate</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: HGTV家居生活频道已经极大地改变了人们对房地产的看法。

examination_example.sentence: Parents need to remind their children that their needs and desires may change over time, said Julie Gurner, a real <highlight>estate</highlight> analyst.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 房地产分析师Julie Gurner表示，父母应该提醒孩子，他们的需求和愿望可能会随着时间的推移而改变。

examination_example.sentence: Younger children should feel like they're choosing their home, said Adam Bailey, a real <highlight>estate</highlight> attorney based in New York.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 纽约房地产律师亚当·贝利表示，年幼的孩子应该觉得他们正在选择自己的家。
